Just like her father,

00:26:06.440 --> 00:26:08.200
will never be bribed by others.

00:26:10.840 --> 00:26:12.040
Wen Pei is right.

00:26:12.720 --> 00:26:15.000
Eagle won’t be easily used.

00:26:15.280 --> 00:26:18.920
But who is the murderer who killed Madam?

00:26:19.360 --> 00:26:21.040
I need to get well soon.

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:24.040
I still have a lot of things to do.

