Shangguan Bao has been in the three realms for decades.

00:26:44.520 --> 00:26:46.200
to easily lure him down the mountain

00:26:46.600 --> 00:26:47.520
and kill him.

00:26:47.760 --> 00:26:49.800
and framed me.

00:26:51.520 --> 00:26:54.040
This must be a well-designed conspiracy.

00:26:56.720 --> 00:26:58.120
And this helper

00:26:59.000 --> 00:27:01.240
must be trusted by Shangguan Bao.

00:27:03.920 --> 00:27:05.200
His identity

00:27:05.920 --> 00:27:07.720
is beyond our imagination.

00:27:08.200 --> 00:27:09.600
According to you,

00:27:10.680 --> 00:27:13.080
if Qinglong Fortress falls into his hands,

00:27:13.760 --> 00:27:15.880
it will be controlled by the Japanese.

00:27:18.200 --> 00:27:20.040
That's too dangerous.

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:26.280
No, I have to

00:27:26.560 --> 00:27:27.640
to the superiors

00:27:27.960 --> 00:27:29.280
and then make plans.

00:27:29.680 --> 00:27:32.800
Time is precious. I'm counting on you.

00:27:33.040 --> 00:27:34.040
Don't worry.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:35.760
Just take care of yourself.

00:27:36.080 --> 00:27:37.560
Leave the rest to me.

00:27:39.720 --> 00:27:40.800
Here.

00:27:53.720 --> 00:27:54.840
Wen Pei.

00:27:55.960 --> 00:27:57.040
Thank you.

00:27:57.320 --> 00:27:58.280
Don't worry.

00:28:38.400 --> 00:28:39.360
Sister.

00:28:39.720 --> 00:28:43.440
There's something I don't understand.

00:28:47.640 --> 00:28:48.520
Go ahead.

00:28:50.640 --> 00:28:51.600
I don't understand

00:28:51.840 --> 00:28:54.200
why she chose such a faraway place

00:28:54.520 --> 00:28:55.720
to kill him?

00:28:56.080 --> 00:28:57.880
He is familiar with Qinglong Fortress.

00:28:58.200 --> 00:29:00.200
There are many opportunities to take action.

00:29:00.640 --> 00:29:04.600
You don't have to fool me out.

00:29:05.120 --> 00:29:06.600
You mean

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:09.960
