00:29:10.800 --> 00:29:11.520
No, no.

00:29:11.800 --> 00:29:12.760
That's not what I meant.

00:29:13.080 --> 00:29:13.880
I...

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:15.480
I just...

00:29:22.920 --> 00:29:23.800
Sister.

00:29:37.560 --> 00:29:40.880
Uncle, I want to ask you something.

00:29:41.440 --> 00:29:42.520
Go ahead, Eagle.

00:29:43.040 --> 00:29:44.160
Who sent the letter

00:29:44.600 --> 00:29:47.400
who sent the letter that disguised as Huo Lang?

00:29:48.880 --> 00:29:51.160
The letter was on the case in the lobby.

00:29:51.520 --> 00:29:54.560
I found it and gave it to your father.

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:57.080
Eagle.

00:29:58.480 --> 00:30:00.480
Does it matter who sent the letter?

00:30:01.240 --> 00:30:03.000
Why did you suddenly ask about this today?

00:30:03.280 --> 00:30:05.760
I just think the person who sent the letter

00:30:06.040 --> 00:30:08.560
has something to do with my father's death.

00:30:12.560 --> 00:30:15.520
There are many people in the hall every day,

00:30:16.400 --> 00:30:18.200
but I was the only one

00:30:19.360 --> 00:30:20.960
that day.

00:30:21.800 --> 00:30:23.440
Only you.

00:30:26.080 --> 00:30:28.480
After that, I asked all the guards on guard

00:30:29.880 --> 00:30:31.480
and I've never seen anyone sending letters.

00:30:33.360 --> 00:30:35.080
His whereabouts are so secretive.

00:30:35.760 --> 00:30:37.680
I think he must be familiar with

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:40.040
He knows the terrain of the fortress very well.

00:30:48.880 --> 00:30:49.840
Eagle.

00:30:51.480 --> 00:30:52.760
At this point,

00:30:53.760 --> 00:30:54.520
I have to remind you

00:30:54.520 --> 00:30:56.040
I have to remind you.

00:30:57.120 --> 00:30:58.080
Go ahead.

00:31:00.280 --> 00:31:02.200
Based on your relationship with Pahra Chae,

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:05.120
he was your fiancé.

00:31:05.520 --> 00:31:07.160
It's inevitable that he still has feelings for you.

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:10.920
But now that he killed your father,

00:31:11.800 --> 00:31:14.040
he has become the enemy of the swordsman.

00:31:15.520 --> 00:31:17.400
I hope you can tell right from wrong.

00:31:17.640 --> 00:31:19.280
[Don't be troubled by love.]

00:31:20.280 --> 00:31:21.960
Avenge your father as soon as possible

00:31:22.320 --> 00:31:24.160
and calm the anger of our brothers.

00:31:25.720 --> 00:31:27.280
and comfort

00:31:28.880 --> 00:31:30.520
your father's soul in heaven.

00:31:31.120 --> 00:31:32.600
You're right.

00:31:33.840 --> 00:31:35.520
I'll keep that in mind.

00:31:36.640 --> 00:31:39.600
From now on, all you care about is revenge.

00:31:41.480 --> 00:31:42.880
I have no other thoughts.

00:32:53.280 --> 00:32:55.480
I will carry on your will

00:32:56.640 --> 00:32:58.400
