00:34:18.480 --> 00:34:20.040
Don’t fall into their trap.

00:34:20.400 --> 00:34:22.920
In the end, you’ll regret your death.

00:34:23.199 --> 00:34:23.960
Shut up!

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:26.920
Eagle, let me explain.

